{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "苏方 第4话 希望的灯火",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕噜噜噜噜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这就是最后一头了……\\n哈啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "呼……总算打倒了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "是啊。半路被一大群魔兽包围的时候\\n我还担心该怎么办才好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这都是多亏了大家的奋战，\\n谢谢你们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不用谢……我倒是想这么说，\\n不过真的好累啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那就找个村子休息一下吧？\\n我记得这附近应该有。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "是啊。\\n有个宁静祥和的好地方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，那我们就去那里吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "咦？这、这无比荒芜的村子，\\n就是那个宁静祥和的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "不、不对……为什么？\\n我以前来的时候不是这样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民1",
            "context": "都是因为魔兽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "魔兽？\\n难道是被魔兽袭击了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民1",
            "context": "嗯。前阵子开始，\\n一群魔兽盘踞在这附近。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民1",
            "context": "那些家伙时不时地袭击过来……\\n已经有很多人丢了性命……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！\\n难道那群魔兽就是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。应该就是刚才\\n和我们战斗过的魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "老婆婆……请放心。\\n我们已经打倒了那些魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民1",
            "context": "哦、噢噢……真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是的。\\n所以这个村子已经安全了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民1",
            "context": "谢谢你们！\\n真的非常感谢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120020_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民1",
            "context": "村民们，你们听到了吗！？\\n这几位好心人救了我们的村子！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民2",
            "context": "啊啊，得救了……\\n再也不用在恐惧中过夜了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民3",
            "context": "太感激了！这样一来我们的田地\\n就不会被魔兽蹂躏了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民3",
            "context": "好！今晚要办祭典庆祝一下！\\n忘记烦恼，尽情狂欢吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "庆祝的祭典吗，真好。\\n那就该你发挥了吧，苏方？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "好，请交给我吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "在这值得庆祝的日子里，\\n我要用仙花焰锦上添花！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "哼……有什么好庆祝的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "嗯？怎么了，小朋友？\\n没了魔兽，你不觉得高兴吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "你们强到可以打倒魔兽对吧？\\n那么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "为什么……\\n为什么没有早点来！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "诶！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "要是你们早点来了的话，\\n爸爸妈妈就不会……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "爸爸妈妈……啊！\\n难道你父母被魔兽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "嗯，是啊！\\n他们为了保护我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "居然说什么要忘记烦恼？\\n我怎么可能忘得掉！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "啊！你等等……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民3",
            "context": "抱、抱歉。都怪我们……\\n说什么要用祭典忘记烦恼。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "不……你们没有错。\\n祭典，就是要在\\n这种时候举办才好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "所以……让我们着手准备祭典吧。\\n各位村民，也请你们帮忙准备。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民3",
            "context": "好、好的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "祭典吗……真希望那个男孩也能\\n开心地参加……但现在还不行吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "是啊。要在短时间内\\n转换心境是很难的。不过……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过？你有什么好主意吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "是的。或许我能\\n制造转换心境的契机。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "用我的……仙花焰！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "于是，祭典之夜……\\n苏方带着那个男孩\\n来到了某个地方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "喂，到底要去哪里啊？\\n先说好，我可不去什么祭典……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "没关系，我们不是去祭典会场。\\n我想带你去的……是这里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "咦？村子附近的山丘上？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我要在这里放仙花焰，\\n想让你在最棒的位置上看到。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "仙花焰……那是什么？\\n莫名其妙……我能回去了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "其实……\\n我的父母也去世了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "诶！？\\n怎、怎么突然说这些……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "那时我的梦想破灭……\\n失去了活下去的意义和希望……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "不过……不，正因如此，\\n我才永远都不会忘记……\\n那时见到的仙花焰。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "仙花焰的美丽光芒在我心中\\n再次点燃了生的希望……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "在心中点燃了希望……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "苏方，差不多该……\\n村民们都在等着仙花焰呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "好的……那我要开始了！\\n去吧，传达到村民们的内心去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "夜空中绽放的，是向着崭新的未来\\n前进的祝福……和安魂祈愿之花！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "这就是我的仙花焰！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "近距离观赏仙花焰的感想如何？\\n其实本来是不可以……\\n在离观众这么近的地方放的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "不过……今天就破例一次。\\n因为我无论如何都想让你看到。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "谢、谢谢你。好漂亮……\\n我第一次看到这种……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "仙花焰真漂亮啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "没错，很漂亮吧。\\n不过……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "只要能活着……\\n就能看到更多美好的事物。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "是吗……希望是这样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "一定没问题的，因为……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "你只是一时迷失了方向……\\n梦想和希望，永远和你同在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}